summary: Avengers END GAME
title: Avengers END GAME
body:
Now that the ban is being lifted I can finally talk about The End Game

As soon as the movie started and I realized that nothing can change what Thanos has done it made me cry instantly and somehow after 5 crazy years Scott Lang came back from Quantum Realm and the final journey began.

Avengers assembled one last time. Thor was depressed yet he came back to save the universe. We traveled through time and boy it was nostalgic to relive the fights from the beginning. They lost, we lost some of the greatest superheroes of all time but at the end we won.

Bruce Banner accepted Hulk finally, Clint took his revenge and got his family back, Steve Rogers got his Happy ending, yes we lost Natasha Romanoff but she was never alone as she used to say, she had a family, The Avengers were and will always be her family.

And finally Tony Stark… all I’m going to say is ‘We love you 3000′

Yes, we lost family, friends and half of the universe but the Avengers never stopped, they never gave up and now we have the Guardians of Galaxy back, Asgard has a new King or should I say Queen. The Wakanda warriors are back, Doctor Strange came back with Spiderman from space and now is ready to begin his new journey.

body:
Okay, you know how in cartoons and movies a person will clean the house and 2 seconds later the kid comes home and there’s mud all over the floor?

What if Tony built a robot that cleans the ceiling and as soon at it finishes, Peter gets home and muds it up again?
